//To have a backup of your database


shut down the Neo4j server.

Create a folder "Neo4jDbBackup" at different location. (This may be any location in your file system).

Copy all the data in the folder of your database to this "Neo4jDbBackup" folder created at different location.

Use any Windows compression/decompression tool like WinZip, 7 Zip, or WinRAR to zip our Database folder.


//This has created the BACKUP and to RESTORE follow the reverse process to copy data to your actual database folder
//from the "Neo4jDbBackup" folder
